   int maxLevel;

      this.action.action(var1, var2, var3, var4, var5);
   }

   public int getMaxLevel(ItemStack var1) {
      return this.canIntegrate && g.isIntegrated(var1) ? this.maxLevel + 1 : this.maxLevel;
   }

   public int getMaxLevel(NBTTagCompound var1) {
      return this.canIntegrate && g.isIntegrated(var1) ? this.maxLevel + 1 : this.maxLevel;
   }

   public double getEnergyToUse() {
      return this.energyToUse;
   }

   public boolean isAdmin() {
      return this == ADMIN;
   }

   public boolean isCapacity() {
      return this == POWER;
   }

      return ADMIN;
   }

   public int getOrdinal() {
      return this.ordinal();
   }

   public rr getType() {
      return rr.ARMOR;
   }

      return this.name();
   }

      return this.name;
   }

      config.save();
   }
